  <p>Besides '<tt>change-info</tt>' (blue), you can also use '<tt>change-success</tt>' (green),
  '<tt>change-danger</tt>' (read), and '<tt>change-warning</tt>' (yellow).</p>

  <h3>Field got added, '<tt>change-new</tt>'</h3>

  <p>Mainly used on INPUT and TEXTAREA element, but may appear with
  other elements as well.  The visualization depends a bit on
  whether the element is required at the moment.</p>

