  <p>The markings disappear when you move away from the select box,
  to indicate that you have noticed the change.</p>

  <h3>Checkboxes</h3>

  <p>Checkbox lists are pretty verbose in Bootstrap's HTML.  They are
  losely connected by their name.  This plugin requires a wrapping
  container when you like to use '<tt>data-pick</tt>' or a change
  description.  The wrapper looks like this:</p>

#fragment/bs5/cbwrap.html.code

  <p>To make the HTML example below easier to read, we have removed
  '<tt>class="form-check-input" type="checkbox"</tt>' from the
  '<tt>&lt;input&gt;</tt>' and '<tt>class="form-check-label"</tt>'
  from each checkbox '<tt>&lt;label&gt;</tt>' in the example below.

<div class="row">
  <div class="col-6">
    <div style="max-height: 18lh; overflow-y: scroll">

#fragment/bs5/cb.html.code

    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="col-6">

  <ul class="nav nav-pills" id="demo-cb">
